{"tid":1179061,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"我恨我係處","createTime":"2019-05-31T00:14:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-31T10:07:12.000Z","uid":228368,"like":7,"dislike":69,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"4e17777c1f52723cb49bed506e2bf0afd7a003b5","tid":1179061,"uid":228368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T00:14:26.000Z","msg":"知道男朋友以前同過啲女朋友做<br />\n我都好想好似佢地咁滿足佢<br />\n但我係處 男朋友一黎覺得處好大責任<br />\n二黎佢同我試過好幾次都入唔到<br />\n我唔係想拎處黎綁住佢<br />\n我只係好想好想 滿足佢 做一個稱職嘅女朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da3851ee4894ce7dde88e6a23c5cab606bb6659e","tid":1179061,"uid":195570,"like":19,"dislike":6,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T00:17:18.000Z","msg":"俾佢屌屎眼再口爆就ok <br />\n含撚爽過屌西"},{"pid":"d1e1a8d4e9541dfcc34e3b78dd31373aa4e49eaa","tid":1179061,"uid":150,"like":50,"dislike":3,"score":47,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T00:22:40.000Z","msg":"你地一齊咗幾耐？<br />\n其實你唔洗咁諗，都唔好話咩盡女朋友責任就要啪啪啪<br />\n你係愛佢，覺得值得，咪俾囉，佢入唔入到去係遲早嘅事，只要你甘願就得。你要諗清楚係咪真係願意咁做先，唔係因為同佢前女友比較，唔係因為你覺得女朋友嘅責任就係要咁做。<br />\n<br />\nbtw佢覺得啪處女大責任？收皮啦佢，佢係愛你，係有責任感嘅男人就唔會講依句野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我有個朋友之前破咗佢ex處，最後不幸分手。<br />\n然後佢話破處女好大責任，以後都唔想識處女，但佢ex其實無話要佢負責任或者迫佢做乜。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />依啲係個人選擇嚟<br />\n反正如果我係樓主，我會睇定啲先，唔好話俾就俾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e88af7fe5a69e87e38d981a9bc2820c176642ef3","tid":1179061,"uid":41368,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T00:38:09.000Z","msg":"我抵諗啲幫你破咗佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n問題解決晒"},{"pid":"f8d2236cf074ad35363d8bbc566e6ac0b734a930","tid":1179061,"ui